如果想增長力高少少，可考慮：華夏恒生科技ETF（3088）、阿里（9988）、騰訊（0700）、港交所（0388）、舜宇光學（2382）、小米（1810）、比亞迪（1211）、中生製藥（1177），但就要明白波動性比上述會高左，同時風險大左，你要自己平衡。<br />\n<br />\n現時大市處合理區，可以一邊投資一邊留現金，而餘下現金的運用，就是等大跌市時出手，如果你能在這段時間學好選股等技巧，到大跌市時就能把握機會，財富增值會更明顯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87/29%e6%ad%b2-%e7%82%92%e7%87%b6%e5%a4%96%e5%8c%af-%e7%8e%a9%e6%99%ba%e8%83%bd%e5%94%ae%e8%b3%a3%e6%a9%9f-%e8%bc%b8%e8%bf%9130%e8%90%ac-%e6%83%b3%e7%9b%a1%e5%bf%ab%e7%bf%bb%e8%ba%ab-207431/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2F%25e6%258a%2595%25e8%25b3%2587%2F29%25e6%25ad%25b2-%25e7%2582%2592%25e7%2587%25b6%25e5%25a4%2596%25e5%258c%25af-%25e7%258e%25a9%25e6%2599%25ba%25e8%2583%25bd%25e5%2594%25ae%25e8%25b3%25a3%25e6%25a9%259f-%25e8%25bc%25b8%25e8%25bf%259130%25e8%2590%25ac-%25e6%2583%25b3%25e7%259b%25a1%25e5%25bf%25ab%25e7%25bf%25bb%25e8%25ba%25ab-207431%2F&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcqP8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=87ae38e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/%e6%8a%95%e8%b3%87/29%e6%ad%b2-%e7%82%92%e7%87%b6%e5%a4%96%e5%8c%af-%e7%8e%a9%e6%99%ba%e8%83%bd%e5%94%ae%e8%b3%a3%e6%a9%9f-%e8%bc%b8%e8%bf%9130%e8%90%ac-%e6%83%b3%e7%9b%a1%e5%bf%ab%e7%bf%bb%e8%ba%ab-207431/</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:06:02.000Z","msg":"無辧法, 無論問乜, 其實佢都係 copy &amp; paste 個答案"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZDeW5qA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZDeW5qA.png&h=cd6ad9db&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c29c2a233b70115c99001667b47194bd97d45718","tid":2322579,"uid":365423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e657d788b2be984da4924ac1c39ff1a6fd73adc8","tid":2322579,"uid":368978,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T12:06:07.000Z","msg":"有美股唔買買港股<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj